Package: tidyheatmaps
Title: Heatmaps From Tidy Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Jan Broder",
           family = "Engler",
           role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           email = "broder.engler@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-3169-2076"))
Description: The goal of 'tidyheatmaps' is to provide a tidyverse-style interface to the powerful heatmap package 'pheatmap' by @raivokolde. This enables the convenient generation of complex heatmaps from tidy data.
